    "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"support-card support-card--wide\">\n  <div class=\"support-top-stripe\"></div>\n  <div class=\"support-inner\">\n\n    <!-- ── Header ── -->\n    <div class=\"support-header\">\n      <div class=\"support-main-title\">헌상 안내<br></div><div class=\"support-sub-title\">위에서부터 순서대로, 완전 정복을 목표로！</div> <div class=\"support-deco-line\">♡ ♡ ♡</div><span class=\"support-accent\">수명이라면 당연히...그렇지？</span>\n      \n    </div>\n    <!-- ── Spread / Tech Section ── -->\n    <div class=\"support-accordion-wrap open\" id=\"acc-spread\">\n      <div class=\"support-accordion-header\" onclick=\"toggleAcc('acc-spread')\">\n        <div class=\"support-sec-head\"><span class=\"support-sec-icon\">⋈</span> 바로 할 수 있는 확산과 기술로 헌상</div>\n        <span class=\"support-accordion-arrow\">▼</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-accordion-body\">\n\n        <!-- ── Clip Request Section ── -->\n        <div class=\"support-clip-request\">\n          <div class=\"support-clip-request__img-wrap\">\n            <img src=\"./assets/切り抜きリクエスト.png\" alt=\"클립 리퀘스트\" class=\"support-clip-request__img\" />\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"support-clip-request__body\">\n            <div class=\"support-clip-request__title\">클립 영상으로 만들어 줬으면 하는 장면을 알려주세요！</div>\n            <div class=\"support-clip-request__desc\">좋아하는 장면의 생방송 링크와 타임스탬프（예：1:20:14）를 보내주시면 클립 영상이 만들어질지도！혼자서 장면을 찾는 건 정말 힘드니까 협력해 주시면 정말 기뻐요！</div>\n            <a class=\"support-clip-request__btn\" href=\"https://marshmallow-qa.com/g2t47f2przg3nzd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">🎬 클립 장면 리퀘스트하기</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"support-spread-list\">\n\n      <div class=\"support-spread-item\">\n        <div class=\"support-pink-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n          <div class=\"support-iname\">활동 홍보하기</div>\n          <div class=\"support-inote\">좋아요와 공유를 통해 YouTube 영상, 생방송, X 게시물을 홍보해 주세요🤍<br>특히, 공유 버튼→복사 버튼을 누르면 아소부의 계정 추천도가 올라가요</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"support-spread-item\">\n        <div class=\"support-pink-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n          <div class=\"support-iname\">콘테스트에 참가하기</div>\n          <div class=\"support-inote\">색칠 콘테스트・일러스트 콘테스트・클립 영상 콘테스트 등에 참가해서 모두 함께 즐기고 싶어요！</div>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"#contest\" onclick=\"event.preventDefault();window.scrollTo(0,0);location.hash='contest'\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"support-spread-item\">\n        <div class=\"support-pink-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n          <div class=\"support-iname\">클립 영상 만들기 / 올리기</div>\n          <div class=\"support-inote\">만든 동영상을 나에게 보내주세요! 내 채널에 게시합니다!</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      </div><!-- /spread-list -->\n      </div><!-- /accordion-body -->\n    </div><!-- /acc-spread -->\n\n    <!-- ── Priority list ── -->\n    <div class=\"support-accordion-wrap open\" id=\"acc-money\">\n      <div class=\"support-accordion-header\" onclick=\"toggleAcc('acc-money')\">\n        <div class=\"support-sec-head\"><span class=\"support-sec-icon\">⋈</span> 어른을 위한 헌상♡</div>\n        <span class=\"support-accordion-arrow\">▼</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-accordion-body\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:1.4em;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.02em;padding:10px 16px 10px 20px;color:#ffffff;border-left:3px solid #ff79b0;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">아소부의 기쁨 랭킹</div>\n        <div class=\"support-list\">\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n      <div class=\"support-item support-top\">\n        <div class=\"support-nbubble\">1</div>\n        <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n          <div class=\"support-iname\">멤버십</div>\n          <div class=\"support-inote\">매달 계속해 주는 게 가장 기뻐요！한정 굿즈 선물도 있어요～</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"support-iright\">월 ¥490～</div>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"#membership\" onclick=\"event.preventDefault();window.scrollTo(0,0);location.hash='membership'\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n      <div class=\"support-item\">\n        <div class=\"support-nbubble\">2</div>\n        <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n          <div class=\"support-iname\">굿즈 구매</div>\n          <div class=\"support-inote\">화면 속만으로는 부족하죠</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"support-iright\">¥750〜</div>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"#goods\" onclick=\"event.preventDefault();window.scrollTo(0,0);location.hash='goods'\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n\n        <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n        <div class=\"support-item\">\n          <div class=\"support-nbubble\">3</div>\n          <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n            <div class=\"support-iname\">슈퍼챗/멤버십 선물</div>\n            <div class=\"support-inote\">라이브 중 언제든지 주세요🖤 하루에 천 엔은 필수！</div>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"support-iright\">¥100~</span>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@MitaraiAsobu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">➡</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n<div class=\"sp-wish\" style=\"margin:24px 0;\"><div class=\"sp-wish__body\"><img class=\"sp-wish__icon\" src=\"./mita/money.png\" alt=\"Mitarai Asobu\"><div class=\"sp-wish__bubble-wrap\"><div class=\"sp-wish__bubble\">헌상헌상～！</div></div></div></div>\n\n    <!-- ── Crowdfunding Note ── -->\n    <div class=\"support-sec-head\"><span class=\"support-sec-icon\">⋈</span> 크라우드펀딩에 대해</div>\n\n    <div class=\"support-goods-box\">\n      <div class=\"support-goods-icon\">💰</div>\n      <div class=\"support-goods-body\">\n        <div class=\"support-goods-title\">어떤 지원이든 크라우드펀딩 금액에 합산됩니다！자세한 내용은 크라펀 페이지를 확인해 주세요。</div>\n        <a class=\"support-clip-request__btn\" href=\"#crowdfunding\" onclick=\"event.preventDefault();window.scrollTo(0,0);location.hash='crowdfunding'\" style=\"margin-top:14px;display:inline-flex;\">🎗 크라펀 페이지 보기</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n      </div><!-- /accordion-body -->\n    </div><!-- /acc-money -->\n\n    <!-- ── Footer ── -->\n    <div class=\"support-footer\">\n      <div class=\"support-footer-hearts\">♡ ♡ ♡</div>\n      <div class=\"support-footer-msg\">응원해주는 당신과 더 즐거운 나날을</div>\n      <div class=\"support-footer-name\">미타라이 아소부</div>\n      <div class=\"support-footer-roman\">Mitarai Asobu</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
  }
